Howto use the ldap java gui
----------------------------

launch: 
/home/admin/tools/ldapbrowser/lbe.sh

Adding a user to the staff (wheel) group

in the group section
right click on cn=staff entry
select edit in the drop down menu
select Edit Entry
Goto the last (for example) memberUid entry
right click on it, and 
select Add Value in the drop down menu
A new empty memberUid shows up
Enter the user login name
click on Apply
